  "description": "A long exposure photograph captures a majestic suspension bridge stretching across a dark body of water under a dramatic twilight or dawn sky. The bridge's towers are silhouetted against a gradient of color, transitioning from a deep reddish-orange at the horizon to a darker grey-blue overhead. The bridge is illuminated with a string of golden lights creating a vibrant line across the water. Dense, dark foliage frames the image on either side, creating a natural vignette and drawing the viewer's eye toward the central subject. The water's surface appears calm, reflecting the subtle hues of the sky. There are a few distant ships visible, adding scale and a sense of activity.",
